data.description: Private access to National Forest from Barranco Canyon! Custom Built Mountain Home with high end off site built Karsten home as the base. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home boasts a large living area, loft with vigas, log banisters, wood stove, and lots of details. Views through the South windows provide majestic Ponderosa Pine, pinon, juniper and diverse wildlife all on this little piece of mountain paradise. Cool, clear mountain water out of  two wells on two separate 4 acre lots. Fencing around the front for your dogs or bring some small livestock. County maintained roads bring you into this secluded canyon with only a hand full of residences surrounded by the wonders of nature. About 20 minutes to the small town of Mountainair or 1.5 hours to Albuquerque. Mountain living at a great value!
